          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1680168106694-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1680168106694-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1680168106694-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>from the oven and add the <strong>Yorkshire pudding batter</strong>, then spread it evenly, with a spoon, to the edges of the tray</p><p>Tip: Be careful – the oil may splash!</p><p>Put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for 20-25 min or until puffed up and golden – this is your <strong>Yorkshire pudding</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, wash the <strong>spinach</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
